<ul>
  <li><strong>Producer:</strong> <a href="http://www.buckeyecoffee.com" target="_blank">Buckeye Coffee Roasters Co. LCC</a>, USA</li>
  <li><strong>Machines:</strong> all models with Fuji PIDs or the 2in1 system (via Bluetooth or USB)</li>
  <li><strong>Connection:</strong> MODBUS RTU via USB; requires the installation of a <a href="/modbus_serial/">serial driver</a></li>
  <li><strong>Features:</strong> logging of environmental temperature (ET), bean temperature (BT) and related rate-of-rise curves</li>
</ul>

<p class="notice--primary"><strong>Watch out!</strong> The new models are equipped with Fuji PXF PIDs instead of the Fuji PXR PIDs that were build-in before. For those new models choose <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Sedona Elite Roaster PXF</code> from the machine menu.</p>
